OL,3,C'Substantial fire risk' found at major
OL,4,CNI hospital
OL,6,FOur Health Correspondent Deborah
OL,7,FMcAleese unpacks issues raised during
OL,8,Fministerial questions.
OL,10,FA fire safety inspection found a
OL,11,F"substantial risk" at two wards in
OL,12,FBelfast's Royal Victoria Hospital,
OL,13,FHealth Minister Mike Nesbitt has said.
OL,15,FThe minister has said the revelation
OL,16,Fwill do "nothing to try and restore
OL,17,Fpublic and political confidence" in
OL,18,Fthe beleaguered Belfast Trust.
