OL,6,FDuring ministerial questions on
OL,7,FMonday, DUP MLA Diane Dodds asked Mr
OL,8,FNesbitt to explain what significant
OL,9,Fconcerns the Northern Ireland Fire and
OL,10,FRescue Service have about the hospital.
OL,12,FShe said: "Do you know when the trust
OL,13,Fwas first advised about these concerns
OL,14,Fand can you confirm that the Fire and
OL,15,FRescue Service is pursuing an
OL,16,Fenforcement notice in relation to
OL,17,Fthis?"
OL,19,FMr Nesbitt told MLAs: "A fire safety
OL,20,Faudit was carried out at the Royal
OL,21,FVictoria Hospital on June 4.
OL,26,@tD@KOUyD@FO]{D@WOU
