OL,6,F"That was by personnel from the
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland Fire and Rescue
OL,8,FService.
OL,10,F"They did so under the Fire and Rescue
OL,11,FService's Northern Ireland Order 2006.
OL,13,F"The outcome of the audit found a
OL,14,Fsubstantial risk at Ward 4 and Ward 7
OL,15,Fwith a score rating that falls within
OL,16,Fthe enforcement notice category."
