OL,6,FThe minister said a follow-up meeting
OL,7,Fhad taken place on June 11 to assist
OL,8,Fthe Belfast Trust in making the
OL,9,F"necessary improvements" with another
OL,10,Fplanned for Tuesday afternoon.
OL,12,FHe added: "I appreciate the pragmatic
OL,13,Fapproach the Fire and Rescue Service
OL,14,Ftakes to working with responsible
OL,15,Fpersons and audited premises to
OL,16,Fmitigate risk.
OL,18,F"In this case the Fire and Rescue
OL,19,FService inspection officers continued
OL,20,Fto do so with the Belfast Trust
OL,21,Fofficials.
