OL,6,F"I accept the point that this does
OL,7,Fnothing to try and restore public and
OL,8,Fpolitical confidence in the Belfast
OL,9,FHealth and Social Care Trust."
OL,11,FEarlier this month, Mr Nesbitt
OL,12,Fconfirmed the trust is facing the
OL,13,Fhighest-level accountability process
OL,14,Ffollowing a critical report into the
OL,15,Fstaff culture at the cardiac surgery
OL,16,Funit in the Royal Victoria Hospital.
