OL,6,FDuring a meeting of the Stormont
OL,7,FHealth Committee it was stated that
OL,8,Fthe report contained allegations of
OL,9,Fbullying of junior staff by more
OL,10,Fsenior staff, heart surgeons working
OL,11,Ffrom home and the throwing of medical
OL,12,Finstruments during operations.
OL,14,FThe trust has also faced criticism for
OL,15,Fdelays in the opening of the new
OL,16,Fmaternity and children's hospitals on
OL,17,Fthe Royal site.
