OL,6,FUlster Unionist MLA Alan Chambers
OL,7,Fasked the minister if he was satisfied
OL,8,Fworks were now progressing
OL,9,Fsatisfactorily on the new children's
OL,10,Fhospital.
OL,12,FMr Nesbitt said: "I can say that I am
OL,13,Fsatisfied with the verbal assurance I
OL,14,Fgot as recently as yesterday that work
OL,15,Fis progressing on the children's
OL,16,Fhospital on time and to budget.
OL,18,F"That said, we are in the foothills of
OL,19,Fa very long building works campaign.
